overview: This series exposes you to how the other half parties down. Featured cover girl Kiara Cole is tired of being ignored. When she tagged along on this trip, she expected sizzling hot sex. It looks like this seductive blonde will have to take matters into her own supple hands. Cecilia Lion, Lexi Dona, Alexis Crystal, Honour May, and Ella Hughes all bring the high-class heat.
title: Vibes 5
